aboratively defined research priorities on a widespread insect-fungus symbiosis. Symbiosis 81: 101\u2013113 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1007\/s13199-020-00686-9\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.1007\/s13199-020-00686-9<\/span><\/a><span>.<\/span><\/div><\/div>","changed_on":1605884246}